   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The eleventh year of the emperor Caesar Nerva Trajanus Augustus Germanicus Dacicus. Has worked for 5 days in fulfillment of his obligations of the same 11th year for work on the embankments in the new six-gate sluice Payni 29 --- to Epeiph 3 on behalf of Karanis, Krates, son of Sokrates and Thaesis, grandson of Myshthes. I, Isidoros, have signed it.</ab>
         </div>
